  <Summary>A crusade forgotten by history, tainted by the mark of the devil. The next chapter of an epic adventure in the Holy Land. In spite of himself, Gauthier has returned to Hierus Halem, both to accompany his sister Sybil, who is seeking the most hideous man on Earth, and to continue the fight against the Qa'dj, whose demonic breath is once again plaguing the land. Unfortunately, the man Sybil is after is Guy of Lusignan, a brutal, fanatical lord whose actions are rekindling the conflict between Christians and Muslims. Caught once again in a world of violence, Gauthier will owe his survival to an old friend...

Note: The digital edition (4/27/2022) for this issue was released after the print edition.</Summary>
